name: Sound of Fractures - No One Knows Me Like You (Three Oscillators Remix)

attributes.trait_type: No One Knows Me Like You (Three Oscillators Remix)

metadata.description:
Three Oscillators is the moniker of Mumbai-based music producer and DJ Brij Dalvi. With a distinct, dreamlike sound that traverses genres without sticking to one for too long, Three Oscillators' music is a diverse mix of music styles inspired by water, space, science fiction and tranquility.

I've been a fan of more alternative forms of dancefloor music for a little while now, and decided to make this remix as an ode to what I've been listening to lately. I'm not known for making dance-friendly tunes that much but making this remix danceable was a no-brainer. Hope you like what you hear and shoutout to Jamie for getting me on board!
metadata.name: No One Knows Me Like You (Three Oscillators Remix) #1
